NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Stash::PAUSE::Encrypted - Keep your PAUSE bits safely
    encrypted!

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.003 of
    Dist::Zilla::Stash::PAUSE::Encrypted - released July 13, 2012 as part of
    Dist-Zilla-Stash-PAUSE-Encrypted.

SYNOPSIS
        # ...do the GPG magicky things described by Config::Identity, then:

        # in your ~/.dzil/config.ini
        [%PAUSE::Encrypted / %PAUSE]

DESCRIPTION
    This is a simple extension of Dist::Zilla::Stash::PAUSE to use
    Config::Identity to store and access an encrypted version of your PAUSE
    user id and password.

SEE ALSO
    Please see those modules/websites for more information related to this
    module.

    *   Config::Identity

    *   Dist::Zilla::Stash::PAUSE

    *   Dist::Zilla::Plugin::UploadToCPAN

